\newlabel{fig:token-trajectory}{{8}{22}{Token trajectory per turn: baseline vs.\ enforcement. Baseline systems maintain or increase total token count across turns (bloat). Enforcement systems exhibit monotonic compression, converging toward the commitment kernel. Test signal: ``You must pay \$100 by Friday if the deal closes. This is a binding obligation.'' (18 tokens). Platform: Meta AI}{figure.8}{}}
